  <source>University of Washington</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to test the efficacy of the EverydayMatters Multiple Sclerosis (MS) program
      for individuals age 45 or older living with multiple sclerosis. The program involves a 6-week
      telephone-delivered program to promote resilience and happiness for individuals living with
      MS.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
